    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Detective Pursuit:</strong> 17th level</em></p>\n<p>When you use a scholar maneuver on a hostile creature, you can force that target to make a Wisdom saving throw against your maneuver save DC. On a failed save, the target is stunned for 1 minute. The target can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success.</p>\n<p>Once you use this feature, you can't do so again until you finish a short or long rest.</p>",
